      "t": "Claude Meets Blackwell Ultra: Anthropic’s Models Now Run on NVIDIA GB300 in Azure",
      "d": "Anthropic’s Claude models in Microsoft Foundry — hosted on Microsoft Azure and running on NVIDIA GB300 Blackwell Ultra GPUs — are now generally available, giving Azure-native enterprises a powerful new way to build autonomous and domain-specific AI agents. As agentic AI continues to drive enterprise innovation and becomes more autonomous, organizations need access to computing [&#8230;]",
